---
title: Deferred index rebuild — state machine (ADR-0062)
---
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Live
  Live --> Deferred: churn threshold crossed
  Deferred --> Rebuilding: off-lock build starts<br/>(reads inputs snapshot)
  Rebuilding --> Swap: new index ready
  Swap --> Live: atomic pointer swap
  note right of Rebuilding
    Reads keep serving the old index
    (no write lock held)
  end note
